_header: The unseely man said of God that him ne rought

BodRawC534.Transcription:
þe unseli man seyde of god þat hym ne rouhtehe got haue
                    godes hate for þe uo þat he urouhtehier nes an trecheri þat
                    nas þat he souhteHa days hede he hyere neys o [ ]yt hes harme he
                    shouhte
